technologies are expensive, only suitable for short-term back-up, frequency
regulation of the grid, and micro-grid applications. There is also the
challenge around stability (some are prone to explode), the longevity of the
units, and environmental disposal of the used products. This webinar will unpack: Speakers to be confirmed